snippet.title: TOKYO GHOUL: re CALL to EXIST - Announcement Trailer | PS4, PC
snippet.description:
Will you eat or be eaten? Get ready to survive to your fullest when Ghouls are pitted against Investigators in TOKYO GHOUL:re CALL to EXIST!  Your character's talents will be the key to your survival in the battlefield.  

Tokyo Ghoul: Call to Exist is coming soon for the PS4 and PC.
